Except that Perl is filter mode.  In Perl<p><pre><code>    while (<FILE>) { print $_; }
</code></pre>
is line by line and efficient.  Perl programmers avoid<p><pre><code>    my @entire_file=<$yourhandle>;
</code></pre>
